1
00:01:44,416 --> 00:01:46,282
[GRUNTS]

2
00:01:49,950 --> 00:01:53,450
- 50 YEARS AGO, IN ORDER
TO STEAL THE SACRED JEWEL,

3
00:01:53,483 --> 00:01:58,417
NARAKU TRICKED INUYASHA
AND KIKYO INTO BETRAYING
ONE ANOTHER.

4
00:01:58,450 --> 00:01:59,850
- DIE, INUYASHA!

5
00:01:59,883 --> 00:02:02,150
- NOW HE GATHERS
THE SACRED JEWEL SHARDS,

6
00:02:02,183 --> 00:02:06,917
AND AS HE DOES SO,
HIS EVIL POWER GROWS.

7
00:02:08,850 --> 00:02:14,050
MIROKU SUFFERS
UNDER NARAKU'S CURSED
WIND TUNNEL IN HIS RIGHT HAND.

8
00:02:14,083 --> 00:02:15,283
- WIND TUNNEL!

9
00:02:15,317 --> 00:02:18,517
- ONE DAY, THE TUNNEL THREATENS
TO DEVOUR MIROKU'S VERY BEING.

10
00:02:18,550 --> 00:02:22,683
HE MUST DESTROY NARAKU
BEFORE THAT HAPPENS.

11
00:02:23,217 --> 00:02:28,158
SANGO'S FATHER AND FELLOW
DEMON SLAYERS WERE KILLED
BEFORE HER VERY EYES.

12
00:02:28,192 --> 00:02:30,125
NARAKU HAD PLAYED A FOUL TRICK,

13
00:02:30,158 --> 00:02:32,525
POSSESSING SANGO'S
BROTHER KOHAKU...

14
00:02:32,558 --> 00:02:33,225
- KOHAKU.

15
00:02:33,258 --> 00:02:34,592
- AND SETTING HIM AGAINST HER.

16
00:02:34,625 --> 00:02:39,525
NARAKU, THE DESPICABLE COWARD
WHO NEVER SULLIES HIS OWN HANDS.

17
00:02:39,558 --> 00:02:43,092
SOMEDAY WE WILL GET HIM.

18
00:03:01,358 --> 00:03:03,825
- SO YOU'RE SUGGESTING
THAT THIS KAGURA WOMAN

19
00:03:03,858 --> 00:03:05,325
MIGHT HAVE BEEN BORN
FROM NARAKU?

20
00:03:05,358 --> 00:03:09,458
- I'M SAYING THAT WE HAVE TO
CONSIDER IT A POSSIBILITY.

21
00:03:09,492 --> 00:03:10,792
- COME ON.

22
00:03:10,825 --> 00:03:13,858
- THAT'S IMPOSSIBLE.
NARAKU'S A MAN.

23
00:03:13,892 --> 00:03:16,358
HOW COULD A MAN
GIVE BIRTH TO A WOMAN?

24
00:03:16,392 --> 00:03:20,558
- NARAKU HIMSELF WAS CREATED
FROM A HOST OF VARIOUS DEMONS.

25
00:03:20,592 --> 00:03:22,958
WHAT IF ONE OF THEM
WAS TORN FROM HIS BODY?

26
00:03:22,992 --> 00:03:26,425
- GOOD POINT, AND SHE COULDN'T
HAVE BEEN NARAKU IN DISGUISE,

27
00:03:26,458 --> 00:03:28,825
SEEING AS SHE KNEW
SO LITTLE ABOUT US.

28
00:03:28,858 --> 00:03:30,892
- IN ANY CASE,
WHATEVER HER STORY MIGHT BE,

29
00:03:30,925 --> 00:03:34,792
IF SHE'S BEEN CREATED
FROM NARAKU, THEN I'M
NOT INTERESTED IN HER.

30
00:03:34,825 --> 00:03:37,325
- WELL, IT'S NOT LIKE YOU'RE
GONNA GO OUT WITH HER.

31
00:03:37,358 --> 00:03:40,358
- COULD YOU TRY AND STAY
FOCUSED, PLEASE, MIROKU?

32
00:03:40,392 --> 00:03:45,392
- SUCH A FOOL.
I ONLY NEED TO CREATE MORE.

33
00:03:53,925 --> 00:03:56,325
[GRUNTING]

34
00:03:59,525 --> 00:04:01,925
- DIE!

35
00:04:03,258 --> 00:04:06,092
- THE WIND SCAR.

36
00:04:08,225 --> 00:04:11,592
- THE WOMAN HAD
THE SAME SCENT AS NARAKU...

37
00:04:11,625 --> 00:04:17,492
AND THE BURN SCAR ON HER BACK
WAS JUST THE SAME AS HIS.

38
00:04:20,858 --> 00:04:24,158
STILL, DON'T YOU THINK IT'S
STRANGE FOR A WOMAN,

39
00:04:24,192 --> 00:04:27,425
THIS KAGURA, POSSESSED
UNUSUAL STRENGTH?

40
00:04:27,458 --> 00:04:29,925
IF NARAKU COULD CREATE
SOMEONE LIKE HER...

41
00:04:29,958 --> 00:04:33,425
- RIGHT. WHY WOULDN'T HE
HAVE DONE SO MUCH EARLIER?

42
00:04:33,458 --> 00:04:37,458
- THAT'S THE POINT.
IT'S NOT THAT HE DIDN'T
CHOOSE TO DO IT...

43
00:04:37,492 --> 00:04:38,792
- HE WASN'T ABLE TO BEFORE.

44
00:04:38,825 --> 00:04:44,892
- MEANING NARAKU HAS RECENTLY
GAINED SOME KIND OF NEW POWERS?

45
00:04:46,125 --> 00:04:48,925
[DISTANT THUNDER]

46
00:04:51,092 --> 00:04:54,058
- WITH THE BLOWS THAT YOU
RECEIVED FROM TETSUSAIGA,

47
00:04:54,092 --> 00:04:58,925
I WAS ABLE TO COMPREHEND
THE POWER OF INUYASHA'S SWORD.

48
00:04:58,958 --> 00:05:02,125
GO FORTH NOW, KAGURA.

49
00:05:03,625 --> 00:05:09,425
YOUR SISTER KANNA HAS
ALREADY BEEN DISPATCHED.

50
00:05:13,992 --> 00:05:16,858
[INSECTS BUZZING]

51
00:05:26,125 --> 00:05:28,458
- WHERE DID THAT WENCH GET TO?!

52
00:05:28,492 --> 00:05:33,492
HOW DARE SHE RESIST
THE KEEPER OF THE OIL'S
YOUNG MASTER?

53
00:05:35,592 --> 00:05:39,525
ONCE YOU FIND KOHARU,
I EXPECT YOU TO BEAT HER.

54
00:05:39,558 --> 00:05:43,058
- WE'LL CONSIDER IT AN HONOR.

55
00:05:45,325 --> 00:05:49,425
[WHIMPERING]
- WHAT COURSE DO I HAVE?

56
00:05:53,225 --> 00:05:55,892
- OVER THERE!

57
00:05:55,925 --> 00:05:57,525
- IT'S HER!

58
00:05:57,558 --> 00:06:00,358
- WE HAVE FOUND KOHARU!

59
00:06:00,392 --> 00:06:02,425
[GRUNTING]

60
00:06:08,125 --> 00:06:08,925
[GASPS]

61
00:06:08,958 --> 00:06:12,625
- WHAT MANNER OF BEING
ARE YOU, WENCH?

62
00:06:13,125 --> 00:06:14,725
- THAT'S EXACTLY
WHAT I WOULD ASK.

63
00:06:14,758 --> 00:06:17,892
YOU SEEM TO BE NO MORE
THAN ORDINARY MEN.

64
00:06:17,925 --> 00:06:21,292
- SHE IS NOT KOHARU, MILORD.

65
00:06:21,325 --> 00:06:24,658
- SUCH BEAUTY.
BRING HER WITH US.

66
00:06:24,692 --> 00:06:25,992
- YES, SIRE.

67
00:06:26,025 --> 00:06:29,325
- YOU WILL COME WITH US.
- RESIST AND YOU SHALL--

68
00:06:29,358 --> 00:06:32,292
- SHE IS IN DANGER.
I MUST HELP.

69
00:06:32,325 --> 00:06:35,225
- NO, YOU DON'T!

70
00:06:40,092 --> 00:06:43,458
AND ONE FOR THE MASTER.

71
00:06:43,492 --> 00:06:45,292
[GROANING]

72
00:06:45,325 --> 00:06:47,358
[HORSE WHINNYING]

73
00:06:47,392 --> 00:06:49,858
- ARE YOU HURT?
- MASTER!

74
00:06:49,892 --> 00:06:51,725
- FORGIVE US, SIRE.

75
00:06:51,758 --> 00:06:53,425
- WE SHALL SEE YOU TREATED.

76
00:06:53,458 --> 00:06:56,258
- THE YOUNG LORD'S FACE
IS BADLY INJURED.

77
00:06:56,292 --> 00:06:59,258
- WHAT WAS THEIR PROBLEM?
- THANK YOU!

78
00:06:59,292 --> 00:07:02,092
- WAS IT YOU THEY WERE AFTER?

79
00:07:02,125 --> 00:07:04,125
- I'M AFRAID SO.

80
00:07:04,158 --> 00:07:05,758
- SANGO!

81
00:07:05,792 --> 00:07:07,792
- SOMETHING WRONG?

82
00:07:07,825 --> 00:07:09,792
- HMM?

83
00:07:10,558 --> 00:07:13,392
[GASPS]
MIROKU!

84
00:07:13,425 --> 00:07:14,325
- HMM?

85
00:07:14,358 --> 00:07:18,225
- IT IS YOU, MASTER MIROKU!
YOU'VE RETURNED!

86
00:07:18,258 --> 00:07:20,992
MIROKU! HOW I'VE MISSED YOU!

87
00:07:21,025 --> 00:07:22,558
- HMM?
- HMM?

88
00:07:22,592 --> 00:07:26,558
- UH...I TAKE IT
WE MET IN THE PAST?

89
00:07:26,592 --> 00:07:28,625
- I AM KOHARU.

90
00:07:28,658 --> 00:07:30,025
- KOHARU...

91
00:07:30,058 --> 00:07:31,425
OH. YOU DON'T SAY?

92
00:07:31,458 --> 00:07:33,958
- FOR 3 LONG YEARS,
I HAVE WAITED.

93
00:07:33,992 --> 00:07:36,658
- KOHARU. I ALMOST DIDN'T
RECOGNIZE YOU.

94
00:07:36,692 --> 00:07:40,192
HOW VERY PROVIDENTIAL,
MEETING YOU LIKE THIS.

95
00:07:40,225 --> 00:07:43,358
- THAT YOUNG GIRL IS
A FRIEND OF MIROKU'S?

96
00:07:43,392 --> 00:07:47,292
- MORE THAN JUST A FRIEND,
JUDGING BY HOW NERVOUS HE LOOKS.

97
00:07:47,325 --> 00:07:48,992
- OH, YEAH!

98
00:07:49,025 --> 00:07:52,692
- I LOST MY PARENTS
AND SIBLINGS IN THE WAR.

99
00:07:52,725 --> 00:07:55,925
THE KEEPER OF THE OIL
TOOK ME UNDER HIS CARE,

100
00:07:55,958 --> 00:07:58,558
BUT WORKED ME DAY AND NIGHT.

101
00:07:58,592 --> 00:08:00,858
I WAS WEARY FROM MY DUTIES,

102
00:08:00,892 --> 00:08:03,992
AND I WEPT EACH NIGHT.

103
00:08:06,392 --> 00:08:09,858
THEN, A WONDROUS DAY.

104
00:08:09,892 --> 00:08:12,158
- HERE. EAT UP.

105
00:08:12,192 --> 00:08:14,292
- A KIND GESTURE FROM YOU,

106
00:08:14,325 --> 00:08:19,625
WHEN YOU HAPPENED BY OUR VILLAGE
TO PERFORM AN EXORCISM.

107
00:08:22,492 --> 00:08:26,358
- SO YOUR NAME IS KOHARU.
AND HOW OLD ARE YOU?

108
00:08:26,392 --> 00:08:28,358
- I'M 11.
- ARE YOU?

109
00:08:28,392 --> 00:08:32,792
KOHARU, WOULD YOU CONSIDER
HAVING MY CHILDREN?

110
00:08:32,825 --> 00:08:34,258
- AAAH!

111
00:08:34,292 --> 00:08:37,058
- UM, IS SOMETHING THE MATTER?

112
00:08:37,092 --> 00:08:38,125
- YOU'RE DISGUSTING!

113
00:08:38,158 --> 00:08:40,958
HOW COULD YOU LEAD
AN INNOCENT GIRL ON LIKE THAT?!

114
00:08:40,992 --> 00:08:41,758
- YOU LETCH!

115
00:08:41,792 --> 00:08:44,325
- THE HAPPIEST DAY OF MY LIFE.
- OH!

116
00:08:44,358 --> 00:08:47,525
- YOU'D BETTER TAKE
RESPONSIBILITY FOR THIS!

117
00:08:47,558 --> 00:08:48,992
- RIGHT.

118
00:08:49,025 --> 00:08:52,058
WOULD IT CHANGE MATTERS
IF I TOLD YOU I HAVEN'T LAID
A FINGER ON THE GIRL?

119
00:08:52,092 --> 00:08:53,992
- THAT SEEMS HARD TO BELIEVE.

120
00:08:54,025 --> 00:08:55,358
- WELL, SHE WAS STILL A CHILD.

121
00:08:55,392 --> 00:09:01,625
- MIROKU HAD TO TAKE LEAVE OF
OUR VILLAGE SHORTLY AFTERWARD.

122
00:09:03,392 --> 00:09:06,892
I KNEW THAT ONE DAY
HE WOULD RETURN FOR ME.

123
00:09:06,925 --> 00:09:11,125
I BELIEVED IT WITH ALL MY HEART.

124
00:09:13,058 --> 00:09:14,225
AS OF LATE,

125
00:09:14,258 --> 00:09:18,792
I NOTICED THE KEEPER
OF THE OIL'S YOUNG LORD
LEERING AT ME.

126
00:09:24,686 --> 00:09:28,592
MY FEARS WERE REALIZED
LAST NIGHT WHEN HE TRIED
TO FORCE HIMSELF ON ME.

127
00:09:28,625 --> 00:09:29,925
- AND THAT'S WHY YOU RAN AWAY?

128
00:09:29,958 --> 00:09:34,458
- YES. I STRUCK HIM
WITH SOME FIREWOOD
UNTIL HE LAY MOTIONLESS.

129
00:09:34,492 --> 00:09:36,158
- OK.

130
00:09:36,192 --> 00:09:40,192
- PLEASE, MIROKU,
WON'T YOU TAKE ME WITH YOU?

131
00:09:40,225 --> 00:09:41,092
- KOHARU.

132
00:09:41,125 --> 00:09:43,258
- I HAVE NOWHERE ELSE TO GO.

133
00:09:43,292 --> 00:09:46,025
BESIDES, I AM AN ADULT NOW.

134
00:09:46,058 --> 00:09:48,258
I AM ABLE TO BEAR YOUR CHILDREN.

135
00:09:48,292 --> 00:09:50,358
[ALL GASP]
- UH, HEH HEH.

136
00:09:50,392 --> 00:09:52,392
- SHE'S EVEN YOUNGER THAN ME.

137
00:09:52,425 --> 00:09:56,158
THINGS REALLY WERE
DIFFERENT BACK THEN.

138
00:10:03,658 --> 00:10:04,592
[SIGHS]

139
00:10:04,625 --> 00:10:07,325
- I HOPE YOU UNDERSTAND
OUR POSITION, MIROKU.

140
00:10:07,358 --> 00:10:09,825
WE CAN'T TAKE THAT GIRL WITH US.

141
00:10:09,858 --> 00:10:10,925
- I KNOW.

142
00:10:10,958 --> 00:10:14,125
- STILL, WE CANNOT SIMPLY
ABANDON THE ORPHANED CHILD.

143
00:10:14,158 --> 00:10:15,392
- TRUE ENOUGH.

144
00:10:15,425 --> 00:10:16,692
PERHAPS SHE CAN ACCOMPANY US

145
00:10:16,725 --> 00:10:20,058
UNTIL WE CAN FIND
A SUITABLE FAMILY
THAT CAN TAKE THE GIRL IN.

146
00:10:20,092 --> 00:10:22,525
- AT THE LEAST,
SEEING IT WAS YOU

147
00:10:22,558 --> 00:10:25,192
WHO ASKED HER
TO BEAR YOUR CHILDREN.

148
00:10:25,225 --> 00:10:26,425
- OH, THAT.

149
00:10:26,458 --> 00:10:29,358
I ASK THE SAME QUESTION
EVERY SINGLE TIME I MEET
A NEW GIRL.

150
00:10:29,392 --> 00:10:33,792
- EVERY GIRL EXCEPT ONE, MAYBE.

151
00:10:34,892 --> 00:10:38,225
- SANGO, WOULD YOU CONSIDER
BEARING MY--

152
00:10:38,258 --> 00:10:41,058
- SPARE ME, WOULD YA?!

153
00:10:44,492 --> 00:10:47,525
- SO MIROKU WAS THE FIRST MAN
YOU FELL IN LOVE WITH?

154
00:10:47,558 --> 00:10:51,025
- HE IS. I REMEMBERED HIM
EVERY DAY THAT PASSED.

155
00:10:51,058 --> 00:10:52,325
I KNEW WE'D MEET AGAIN,

156
00:10:52,358 --> 00:10:56,592
AND THE THOUGHT
OF THAT HELPED ME
THROUGH THE HARD TIMES.

157
00:10:56,625 --> 00:10:58,692
- THAT'S FIRST LOVE.

158
00:10:58,725 --> 00:11:00,258
- I AM SO HAPPY.

159
00:11:00,292 --> 00:11:03,258
SO HAPPY I COULD DIE.

160
00:11:18,925 --> 00:11:20,958
[BUZZING]

161
00:11:38,958 --> 00:11:41,792
[COW LOWS]

162
00:11:41,825 --> 00:11:45,125
[ROOSTER CROWS]

163
00:11:46,858 --> 00:11:49,358
- SUCH A PITY.
POOR YOUNG CHILD.

164
00:11:49,392 --> 00:11:54,392
- SO, WOULD YOU BE WILLING
TO TAKE THIS YOUNG GIRL
INTO YOUR VILLAGE, ELDER?

165
00:11:54,425 --> 00:11:55,758
- I WOULD BE HONORED.

166
00:11:55,792 --> 00:11:58,625
LEAVE THE GIRL WITH ME,
YOUNG MONK.

167
00:11:58,658 --> 00:12:01,558
- PLEASE. I PROMISE
NOT TO BE A BURDEN.

168
00:12:01,592 --> 00:12:02,825
LET ME COME.
- NO CHANCE.

169
00:12:02,858 --> 00:12:05,958
- IT WOULD BE DANGEROUS FOR YOU
TO COME ALONG WITH US.

170
00:12:05,992 --> 00:12:07,792
- STOP ARGUING AND STAY BEHIND.

171
00:12:07,825 --> 00:12:11,358
- IT IS IN YOUR BEST INTEREST.
- SHE'S RIGHT.

172
00:12:11,392 --> 00:12:12,792
- HMM.

173
00:12:12,825 --> 00:12:14,058
- PLEASE, KOHARU.

174
00:12:14,092 --> 00:12:18,025
- I HAVE SPOKEN
TO THE VILLAGE ELDER.

175
00:12:18,992 --> 00:12:21,025
- MIROKU.

176
00:12:21,492 --> 00:12:24,925
- KOHARU, COME WITH ME,
WOULD YOU?

177
00:12:32,325 --> 00:12:37,558
- MIROKU, I CANNOT BEAR
TO BE PARTED AGAIN
AFTER SUCH A SHORT TIME.

178
00:12:37,592 --> 00:12:40,058
- TRY TO UNDERSTAND, KOHARU.

179
00:12:40,092 --> 00:12:45,658
I CANNOT GUARANTEE THAT I WOULD
ALWAYS BE ABLE TO PROTECT YOU
IN TIMES OF BATTLE.

180
00:12:45,692 --> 00:12:51,425
YOU SEE, THE DEMON I PURSUE IS
MORE DEVIOUS AND FORMIDABLE
THAN ANY OTHER.

181
00:12:51,458 --> 00:12:56,525
PARTING LIKE THIS IS
DIFFICULT FOR ME, AS WELL.

182
00:12:56,558 --> 00:12:57,625
[SOBBING]

183
00:12:57,658 --> 00:13:00,692
- DOES IT LOOK LIKE HE'S
SETTING HER STRAIGHT?

184
00:13:00,725 --> 00:13:03,758
- FROM UP HERE, IT LOOKS MORE
LIKE HE'S SEDUCING HER.

185
00:13:03,792 --> 00:13:05,725
- LECHER.
HE'S ALL OVER THE GIRL.

186
00:13:05,758 --> 00:13:09,358
A PARTING LIKE THAT WILL
MAKE HER FALL DEEPER IN LOVE.

187
00:13:09,392 --> 00:13:11,158
WHY ARE YOU STARING?

188
00:13:11,192 --> 00:13:13,292
- I MIGHT JUST BE
IMAGINING IT, SANGO,

189
00:13:13,325 --> 00:13:17,058
BUT IS THERE A LITTLE
JEALOUSY THING GOING ON HERE?

190
00:13:17,092 --> 00:13:19,658
- IT'S YOUR IMAGINATION!

191
00:13:19,692 --> 00:13:20,858
- WHOA!

192
00:13:20,892 --> 00:13:24,125
- IF YOU SAY SO.

193
00:13:27,492 --> 00:13:28,692
- MIROKU, I'M BEGGING YOU.

194
00:13:28,725 --> 00:13:31,558
WON'T YOU STAY WITH ME
ONE LAST NIGHT?

195
00:13:31,592 --> 00:13:33,158
- YOU HEARD KOHARU.

196
00:13:33,192 --> 00:13:36,025
WON'T YOU PLEASE STAY
THE NIGHT WITH US?

197
00:13:36,058 --> 00:13:38,992
- NO. I FEAR THAT
POSTPONING OUR DEPARTURE

198
00:13:39,025 --> 00:13:42,692
WILL ONLY MAKE IT
THAT MUCH HARDER FOR HER.

199
00:13:42,725 --> 00:13:44,658
[SOBBING]

200
00:13:44,692 --> 00:13:48,725
- STAY FOR HER SAKE.
ONE LAST NIGHT WON'T MAKE
THAT MUCH DIFFERENCE.

201
00:13:48,758 --> 00:13:53,058
- IT WOULD PROBABLY HELP,
SEEING AS WE'RE THE ONLY
PEOPLE HERE SHE KNOWS.

202
00:13:53,092 --> 00:13:54,225
- I MUST DECLINE.

203
00:13:54,258 --> 00:13:57,458
IF REASON GAVE WAY TO PASSION
AND KOHARU BECAME PREGNANT,

204
00:13:57,492 --> 00:14:01,858
SHE WOULD BE BURDENED
FOR THE REST OF HER LIFE
WITH MY LIKENESS.

205
00:14:01,892 --> 00:14:02,725
[ALL GASP]

206
00:14:02,758 --> 00:14:04,692
- REASON GAVE WAY TO PASSION?

207
00:14:04,725 --> 00:14:07,325
SO WHAT DOES THAT MEAN, MIROKU?

208
00:14:07,358 --> 00:14:08,458
- DELIGHTED YOU ASKED.

209
00:14:08,492 --> 00:14:10,192
- I'M DELIGHTED
YOU WON'T ANSWER!

210
00:14:10,225 --> 00:14:12,958
SHIPPO'S STILL YOUNG,
REMEMBER?!

211
00:14:12,992 --> 00:14:14,925
[KOHARU CRYING]

212
00:14:14,958 --> 00:14:17,325
[SIGHS]
- SHE'S CRYING.

213
00:14:17,358 --> 00:14:21,725
TSK. SHE SHOULDN'T WASTE
HER TEARS ON THAT CREEP.

214
00:14:21,758 --> 00:14:23,992
- INUYASHA?

215
00:14:24,025 --> 00:14:27,592
- FINE! WE'LL STAY HERE TONIGHT
AND SET OUT IN THE MORNING.

216
00:14:27,625 --> 00:14:31,058
BUT NO TEARS IN
THE MORNING, ALL RIGHT?

217
00:14:31,092 --> 00:14:33,825
[GASPS]
- YES!

218
00:14:33,858 --> 00:14:36,325
- WOW.

219
00:14:46,051 --> 00:14:50,218
- MIROKU, HOW IS
THE BATH TEMPERATURE?

220
00:14:50,251 --> 00:14:52,351
- PERFECT. NICE AND HOT.

221
00:14:52,384 --> 00:14:53,784
- AFTER YOU FINISH YOUR BATH,

222
00:14:53,818 --> 00:14:56,999
I SHALL DO MY BEST
TO PREPARE THE FINEST DINNER
FOR YOU AND YOUR FRIENDS.

223
00:14:57,032 --> 00:15:00,999
- THANKS FOR GOING
TO ALL THIS TROUBLE.

224
00:15:14,566 --> 00:15:16,532
- HUH?

225
00:15:41,099 --> 00:15:43,532
- THIS STEW IS INCREDIBLE!

226
00:15:43,566 --> 00:15:45,399
- YOU SAID IT.

227
00:15:45,432 --> 00:15:47,099
KOHARU REALLY IS A SWEETIE.

228
00:15:47,132 --> 00:15:53,499
IT LOOKS LIKE SHE REALLY WENT
OUT OF HER WAY TO PLEASE YOU
WITH HER COOKING, MIROKU.

229
00:15:54,399 --> 00:15:56,266
WHAT'S WRONG?

230
00:15:56,299 --> 00:15:57,932
- WE'RE SURROUNDED.

231
00:15:57,966 --> 00:15:59,332
- PARDON?

232
00:15:59,366 --> 00:16:03,032
- I FEAR THE MEAL KOHARU TOOK
SO MUCH TROUBLE TO PREPARE
WILL GO COLD.

233
00:16:03,066 --> 00:16:04,199
- YEAH.

234
00:16:04,232 --> 00:16:07,332
STRANGE,THOUGH, THAT THERE'S
NO SCENT OF DEMONS IN THE AIR.

235
00:16:07,366 --> 00:16:10,899
- LET'S GO SURVEY THE AREA.

236
00:16:12,699 --> 00:16:14,899
- HUH?

237
00:16:23,166 --> 00:16:26,466
- GET THEM! HURRY!

238
00:16:32,232 --> 00:16:34,399
- IDENTIFY YOURSELVES.

239
00:16:34,432 --> 00:16:36,332
[GROWLING]

240
00:16:36,366 --> 00:16:39,132
- KILL THEM!

241
00:16:39,166 --> 00:16:40,832
- KILL THEM!

242
00:16:40,866 --> 00:16:42,832
- GET THEM! HURRY!

243
00:16:42,866 --> 00:16:44,732
- ARE YOU FROM THE VILLAGE?

244
00:16:44,766 --> 00:16:47,666
- THEY SEEM TO BE UNDER
SOME KIND OF SPELL.

245
00:16:47,699 --> 00:16:50,299
[ALL SHOUTING]

246
00:16:50,332 --> 00:16:51,599
- UNH!

247
00:16:51,632 --> 00:16:53,666
I DON'T THINK SO!

248
00:16:53,699 --> 00:16:55,332
AAH!

249
00:17:02,099 --> 00:17:04,199
- UNH! INUYASHA!

250
00:17:04,232 --> 00:17:07,532
THEY ARE ONLY MORTALS,
NOT DEMONS!

251
00:17:07,566 --> 00:17:10,966
- YEAH, I FIGURED THAT MUCH OUT!

252
00:17:21,599 --> 00:17:23,199
- WHAT'S GOING ON OUT THERE?

253
00:17:23,232 --> 00:17:26,332
- THEIR NUMBERS ARE GREAT.
I SHALL ASSIST THEM.

254
00:17:26,366 --> 00:17:28,599
- SOMETHING DREADFUL
HAS HAPPENED!

255
00:17:28,632 --> 00:17:29,999
- WHAT'S THE MATTER, KOHARU?

256
00:17:30,032 --> 00:17:34,199
- A DEMON GOT INSIDE
AND ATTACKED THE ELDER
AND HIS WIFE.

257
00:17:34,232 --> 00:17:38,232
[GRUNTS, CLEARS THROAT]

258
00:17:50,232 --> 00:17:52,299
- ARE THEY REALLY DEAD?

259
00:17:52,332 --> 00:17:53,766
- THE POOR ELDER.

260
00:17:53,799 --> 00:17:55,166
- A DEMON DID THIS?

261
00:17:55,199 --> 00:17:57,999
- THINK. DO YOU REMEMBER
WHAT THE DEMON LOOKED LIKE?

262
00:17:58,032 --> 00:18:01,866
- NOT EXACTLY.
I ONLY CAUGHT A GLIMPSE OF IT.

263
00:18:01,899 --> 00:18:03,799
- BUT ONE THING
DOESN'T MAKE SENSE.

264
00:18:03,832 --> 00:18:08,166
WHY DIDN'T INUYASHA
AND MIROKU SENSE A DEMON?

265
00:18:10,532 --> 00:18:12,499
- HUH?

266
00:18:13,366 --> 00:18:16,432
THERE IT IS!
[GRUNTS]

267
00:18:17,132 --> 00:18:18,799
HUH? SHE VANISHED!

268
00:18:18,832 --> 00:18:21,466
- HUH?

269
00:18:29,499 --> 00:18:32,266
- HUH?
[GASPS]

270
00:18:38,866 --> 00:18:41,899
HIRAIKOTSU!

271
00:18:52,380 --> 00:18:54,280
AAAH!

272
00:18:57,780 --> 00:19:01,447
- SANGO! SHIPPO!
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

273
00:19:01,480 --> 00:19:04,180
SANGO! SAY SOMETHING!

274
00:19:04,213 --> 00:19:06,547
HMM?

275
00:19:07,513 --> 00:19:08,413
- KAGOME.

276
00:19:08,447 --> 00:19:10,980
- THAT YOUNG GIRL IS THE DEMON?

277
00:19:11,013 --> 00:19:13,780
KOHARU! WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

278
00:19:13,813 --> 00:19:16,347
[GRUNTING]

279
00:19:17,280 --> 00:19:20,647
- LOOK INTO MY MIRROR.
GIVE YOUR SOUL.

280
00:19:20,680 --> 00:19:23,180
- HUH...

281
00:19:45,780 --> 00:19:47,880
- INUYASHA! USE RESTRAINT!

282
00:19:47,913 --> 00:19:50,347
THE VILLAGERS ARE UNDER
SOMEONE'S SPELL.

283
00:19:50,380 --> 00:19:53,113
WE MUST NOT HARM THEM.

284
00:19:56,947 --> 00:19:59,547
- WE AREN'T GETTING ANYWHERE!

285
00:19:59,580 --> 00:20:03,880
- YOU FOOLS ARE SO PATHETIC.

286
00:20:03,913 --> 00:20:04,813
- HMM?

287
00:20:04,847 --> 00:20:07,013
- YOU WOULD HAVE DONE WELL
TO SLAY THEM ALL.

288
00:20:07,047 --> 00:20:09,747
THAT WAY, THEY WOULDN'T
KEEP COMING AFTER YOU.

289
00:20:09,780 --> 00:20:11,347
- KAGURA.
- NOT YOU AGAIN.

290
00:20:11,380 --> 00:20:14,947
- THEN AGAIN, I SUPPOSE
IF YOU WERE CAPABLE
OF SLAYING THEM,

291
00:20:14,980 --> 00:20:16,547
YOU WOULD HAVE ALREADY DONE SO.

292
00:20:16,580 --> 00:20:19,847
- ARE YOU THE ONE WHO HAS
POSSESSED THESE VILLAGERS?

293
00:20:19,880 --> 00:20:20,947
- I AM.

294
00:20:20,980 --> 00:20:24,113
A MORTAL WITH NO SOUL IS
NO DIFFERENT FROM A DEAD MAN.

295
00:20:24,147 --> 00:20:25,247
- MORTAL WITH NO SOUL?

296
00:20:25,280 --> 00:20:28,880
- YOUR FRIEND KAGOME IS HAVING
THE SOUL SUCKED OUT OF HER

297
00:20:28,913 --> 00:20:30,480
EVEN AS WE SPEAK.

298
00:20:30,513 --> 00:20:31,713
- YOU WITCH!

299
00:20:31,747 --> 00:20:35,113
- THAT MUST MEAN THAT THERE'S
A SECOND DEMON HERE WITH KAGURA.

300
00:20:35,580 --> 00:20:38,347
- INUYASHA, UNSHEATH
YOUR TETSUSAIGA.

301
00:20:38,380 --> 00:20:41,780
THIS TIME,
VICTORY SHALL BE MINE!

302
00:20:41,813 --> 00:20:42,713
- KAGOME.

303
00:20:42,747 --> 00:20:44,180
- WHAT AILS YOU, INUYASHA?

304
00:20:44,213 --> 00:20:45,880
DON'T TELL ME YOU'RE AFRAID.

305
00:20:45,913 --> 00:20:46,913
[SNORTS]

306
00:20:46,947 --> 00:20:49,347
- MIROKU, GO BACK TO THE HOUSE
AND HELP THE GIRLS.

307
00:20:49,380 --> 00:20:51,747
- OF COURSE I WILL.
WHAT ABOUT YOU?

308
00:20:51,780 --> 00:20:54,413
- YOU KNOW WHAT.

309
00:20:56,180 --> 00:20:59,547
I'M STAYING HERE
TO FINISH THIS WITCH OFF.

310
00:20:59,580 --> 00:21:00,513
- HMM.

311
00:21:00,547 --> 00:21:02,847
[SHOUTS]

312
00:21:09,480 --> 00:21:12,080
- GO NOW, MIROKU!

313
00:21:12,113 --> 00:21:14,747
- I'M ON MY WAY!

314
00:21:15,013 --> 00:21:19,047
- YOUR HELP
WILL ARRIVE TOO LATE!

315
00:21:28,147 --> 00:21:30,880
- THANK YOU, KILLALA.

316
00:21:35,647 --> 00:21:36,913
HUH?

317
00:21:36,947 --> 00:21:38,780
KOHARU! KOHARU!

318
00:21:38,813 --> 00:21:42,047
SAY SOMETHING! KOHARU!

319
00:21:43,680 --> 00:21:45,880
- HMM?

320
00:21:45,913 --> 00:21:48,613
[GASPS]
MIROKU, IT WAS HORRID!

321
00:21:48,647 --> 00:21:52,480
- I'M HERE FOR YOU.
YOU'RE IN SAFE HANDS NOW.

322
00:21:52,513 --> 00:21:54,547
[GROANING]

323
00:21:54,580 --> 00:21:56,980
- HUH?

324
00:21:57,913 --> 00:22:01,980
STOP! WHAT ARE YOU DOING
TO MY FRIEND?

325
00:22:03,580 --> 00:22:04,880
OH!

326
00:22:04,913 --> 00:22:07,880
[GROANING]

327
00:22:20,147 --> 00:22:21,513
[SINGING IN JAPANESE]

328
00:23:57,508 --> 00:24:00,928
- NARAKU CREATES KAGURA
AND KANNA FROM HIS OWN BODY.

329
00:24:00,962 --> 00:24:03,995
A SHARD OF THE SACRED JEWEL
GLIMMERS IN NARAKU'S HAND.

330
00:24:04,028 --> 00:24:07,495
THAT'S THE VERY SAME SHARD
KIKYO STOLE FROM ME.

331
00:24:07,528 --> 00:24:09,028
HOW DID NARAKU GET
HIS HANDS ON IT?

332
00:24:09,062 --> 00:24:14,328
INUYASHA LOSES THE TETSUSAIGA
IN THE FIERCE WINDS CREATED
BY KAGURA.

333
00:24:14,362 --> 00:24:16,928
BETWEEN MIROKU'S WIND TUNNEL
AND MY SACRED ARROW,

334
00:24:16,962 --> 00:24:20,095
WE WILL STOP NARAKU
THIS TIME FOR CERTAIN.

335
00:24:20,128 --> 00:24:23,462
NEXT TIME,
"THE WIND SCAR FAILS."

336
00:24:23,495 --> 00:24:24,495
SEE YOU SOON!

